Name: Snapped
Title: Gloria Aiken
Desc: After leads dry up in a missing person case, a severed body part's discovery reopens investigations.
LongDescription: After leads dry up in a missing person case, detectives in Ennis,Texas, discover a severed body part at a nearby lake; after confirming the DNA match, they begin to uncover the rippling relationship that led to the death of a beloved father.
